============================================================================
    OpenFISMA INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
============================================================================
/*  Software Pre-Requisites  */
------------------------------
* Apache 2 or greater
* PHP 5 or greator
* MySQL 5 or greator
NOTE: Example Apache configuration files 
      is included in the conf directory.

/* OpenFISMA Setup */
--------------------
  a: Download the latest version of OpenFISMA
     $ wget https://openfisma.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/openfisma/tags/openfisma-x.x.x.tar.gz
  b: Install to the directory of choice (/opt/openfisma)
     $ tar -zxvf openfisma-x.x.x.tar.gz
  c: Symlink the apache root directory to the public directory for OpenFISMA
	 $ ln -s /opt/openfisma/public /var/www/html 
  d: Run the web installation script
     > Browse to http://<host_address>/install/index.php
     > Follow the wizard through the installation steps

/* Security Hardening */
------------------------------
  a: REMOVE the /public/install directory after successfully installation.
  b: MAKE /public/mainfile.php only readable by Apache daemon.
     $ chmod 440 /public/mainfile.php
